@startuml
title Flash Home - Coffee Machine Payment System Connectivity

actor User
participant "Home Assistant\nUI" as HA
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "Coffee Machine\nClient" as CoffeeClient
participant "Coffee Machine\nFlash Server" as CoffeeFlash
participant "Provider\nFlash Server" as ProviderFlash
participant "MongoDB\n(Coffee)" as MongoCoffee
participant "MongoDB\n(Provider)" as MongoProvider
participant "Private IOTA\nTestnet (IRI)" as IOTA

== Channel Initialization ==
User -> HA: Initialize Flash Channel
activate HA
HA -> MQTT: Publish initialize command
activate MQTT
MQTT -> CoffeeClient: Forward initialize command
activate CoffeeClient
CoffeeClient -> CoffeeFlash: Initialize channel request
activate CoffeeFlash
CoffeeFlash -> MongoCoffee: Store channel state
activate MongoCoffee
MongoCoffee --> CoffeeFlash: Confirmation
deactivate MongoCoffee
CoffeeFlash -> ProviderFlash: Channel setup negotiation
activate ProviderFlash
ProviderFlash -> MongoProvider: Store channel state
activate MongoProvider
MongoProvider --> ProviderFlash: Confirmation
deactivate MongoProvider
ProviderFlash --> CoffeeFlash: Setup confirmed
CoffeeFlash -> IOTA: Create channel on Tangle
activate IOTA
IOTA --> CoffeeFlash: Channel created
deactivate IOTA
CoffeeFlash --> CoffeeClient: Channel initialized
deactivate CoffeeFlash
CoffeeClient -> MQTT: Publish status update
MQTT -> HA: Forward status update
deactivate CoffeeClient
HA -> User: Display channel status
deactivate MQTT
deactivate HA

== Funding Channel ==
User -> HA: Fund Flash Channel
activate HA
HA -> MQTT: Publish fund command
activate MQTT
MQTT -> CoffeeClient: Forward fund command
activate CoffeeClient
CoffeeClient -> CoffeeFlash: Fund channel request
activate CoffeeFlash
CoffeeFlash -> IOTA: Transfer IOTA tokens
activate IOTA
IOTA --> CoffeeFlash: Transfer confirmed
deactivate IOTA
CoffeeFlash -> MongoCoffee: Update channel balance
activate MongoCoffee
MongoCoffee --> CoffeeFlash: Balance updated
deactivate MongoCoffee
CoffeeFlash -> ProviderFlash: Notify funding
activate ProviderFlash
ProviderFlash -> MongoProvider: Update balance
activate MongoProvider
MongoProvider --> ProviderFlash: Updated
deactivate MongoProvider
ProviderFlash --> CoffeeFlash: Acknowledged
deactivate ProviderFlash
CoffeeFlash --> CoffeeClient: Funding complete
deactivate CoffeeFlash
CoffeeClient -> MQTT: Publish balance update
MQTT -> HA: Forward balance update
deactivate CoffeeClient
HA -> User: Display updated balance
deactivate MQTT
deactivate HA

== Making Coffee (Payment Flow) ==
User -> HA: Make Coffee
activate HA
HA -> MQTT: Publish make_coffee command
activate MQTT
MQTT -> CoffeeClient: Forward make_coffee command
activate CoffeeClient
CoffeeClient -> CoffeeClient: Simulate brewing
CoffeeClient -> CoffeeFlash: Initiate payment transaction
activate CoffeeFlash
CoffeeFlash -> MongoCoffee: Read current state
activate MongoCoffee
MongoCoffee --> CoffeeFlash: Current state
deactivate MongoCoffee
CoffeeFlash -> ProviderFlash: Send signed transaction
activate ProviderFlash
ProviderFlash -> ProviderFlash: Validate signature
ProviderFlash -> MongoProvider: Update state
activate MongoProvider
MongoProvider --> ProviderFlash: State updated
deactivate MongoProvider
ProviderFlash -> ProviderFlash: Sign transaction
ProviderFlash --> CoffeeFlash: Counter-signed transaction
deactivate ProviderFlash
CoffeeFlash -> MongoCoffee: Update channel state
activate MongoCoffee
MongoCoffee --> CoffeeFlash: State saved
deactivate MongoCoffee
CoffeeFlash --> CoffeeClient: Payment confirmed
deactivate CoffeeFlash
CoffeeClient -> MQTT: Publish coffee_made event
MQTT -> HA: Forward coffee_made event
deactivate CoffeeClient
HA -> User: Display coffee ready
deactivate MQTT
deactivate HA

== Closing Channel ==
User -> HA: Close Flash Channel
activate HA
HA -> MQTT: Publish close command
activate MQTT
MQTT -> CoffeeClient: Forward close command
activate CoffeeClient
CoffeeClient -> CoffeeFlash: Close channel request
activate CoffeeFlash
CoffeeFlash -> ProviderFlash: Initiate settlement
activate ProviderFlash
ProviderFlash -> ProviderFlash: Sign final state
ProviderFlash --> CoffeeFlash: Final settlement signature
deactivate ProviderFlash
CoffeeFlash -> IOTA: Settle final balances on Tangle
activate IOTA
IOTA --> CoffeeFlash: Settlement confirmed
deactivate IOTA
CoffeeFlash -> MongoCoffee: Close channel record
activate MongoCoffee
MongoCoffee --> CoffeeFlash: Record closed
deactivate MongoCoffee
CoffeeFlash -> ProviderFlash: Notify closure
activate ProviderFlash
ProviderFlash -> MongoProvider: Close channel record
activate MongoProvider
MongoProvider --> ProviderFlash: Record closed
deactivate MongoProvider
ProviderFlash --> CoffeeFlash: Closure acknowledged
deactivate ProviderFlash
CoffeeFlash --> CoffeeClient: Channel closed
deactivate CoffeeFlash
CoffeeClient -> MQTT: Publish closure status
MQTT -> HA: Forward closure status
deactivate CoffeeClient
HA -> User: Display channel closed
deactivate MQTT
deactivate HA

@enduml
